                            <comment id="13295034" author="nspiegelberg" created="Thu, 14 Jun 2012 13:57:52 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;jitter + exponential backoff?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13295968" author="eclark" created="Fri, 15 Jun 2012 22:31:31 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=nspiegelberg&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;nspiegelberg&quot;&gt;Nicolas Spiegelberg&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
The client already has a semi exponential back off so I just added a jitter that was up to 1% of the previously calculated value.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Also added a test.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
